Order Fulfillment Administrator (FISHER/201404/01/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007326
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Apr 3 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Responsible for Order Fulfillment of direct order placed by Local Business Partners or by trade customers via Local Business Partner.
Perform order entry and screening for export compliance.
Coordinate customer expectations from order receipt to deliver as well as resolve after sales issue arising.
Liaise with Purchasing and Warehouse for supply, packaging and delivery.
Provide single point customer service contact to customers or Local Business Partners and Sales Offices in Asia Pacific.
Specialize in assigned KRA or critical KPI as determined by manager-in-charge.
Requirements:
Diploma or Degree in Engineering or Information Technology.
Preferably with shipping knowledge and logistics coordination experience.
Ability to process Letter of Credit documentation preferred.